definitions.definition: A characteristic manner or style of preparing food , often associated with a place of origin .
examples: French cuisine is considered to be one of the world's most refined and elegant styles of cooking.
The restaurant is noted for its excellent cuisine .

definitions.definition: The food prepared using such style.
Synonym of culinary art : The art of preparing food in general.

main_definition: ( countable , uncountable ) A characteristic manner or style of preparing food , often associated with a place of origin .
secondary_definitions: ( countable , uncountable ) The food prepared using such style.
( uncountable ) Synonym of culinary art : The art of preparing food in general.
